ual attraction.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":1.9485,"vote_count":1792,"poster_path":"/2dMX1NIgT4JEHqck5eflp6tRaCc.jpg","release_date":"2001-01-26","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/h6D695KwxdjFWteDwZ6LHOfICr6.jpg","original_title":"The Wedding Planner","original_language":"en"},{"id":2058,"adult":false,"title":"Addicted to Love","video":false,"overview":"Good-natured astronomer Sam is devastated when the love of his life leaves him for a suave Frenchman. He therefore does what every other normal dumpee would do — go to New York and set up home in the abandoned building opposite his ex-girlfriend's apartment, wait until she decides to leave her current lover, and then win her back.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":1.3895,"vote_count":437,"poster_path":"/sRfuSc6E9GvVaOHdPv4vG3ywfMw.jpg","release_date":"1997-05-23","vote_average":6.145,"backdrop_path":"/35b11n97MKmmkjJoJcx8tqHIVJ2.jpg","original_title":"Addicted to Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":2064,"adult":false,"title":"While You Were Sleeping","video":false,"overview":"A transit worker pulls commuter Peter off railway tracks after he's mugged, but—while he's in a coma—his family mistakenly thinks she's Peter's fiancée, and she doesn't correct them. Things get more complicated when she falls for his brother, who's not quite sure that she's who she claims to be.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"popularity":3.1071,"vote_count":1963,"poster_path":"/qNGO3ETcNwlWqK2kNRpbJSJRlos.jpg","release_date":"1995-04-21","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/gCYvQJ1MhyK4kYFnjpNbNqQtaYc.jpg","original_title":"While You Were Sleeping","original_language":"en"},{"id":251626,"adult":false,"title":"Hasee Toh Phasee","video":false,"overview":"On the eve of Nikhil and Karishma’s engagement, Karishma’s wealthy father, Devesh Solanki, expresses his disapproval, believing Nikhil to be a lackadaisical young man. With one week to prove himself worthy to marry Karishma, Nikhil and Karishma's sister, Meeta, grow closer to each other."